Growing up, the fine arts and more specifically painting became my greatest passion. I would spend hours a day perfecting a painting and making sure every detail was to my liking. My easel was my sanctuary and my safe place. It truly felt like the only place I could be 100% myself, 100% unfiltered. Through art, I found my voice and my confidence and learned what being unfiltered truly meant. I discovered the kind of woman I wanted to become, and I discovered what beauty truly meant to me.My time spent painting taught me that while the visible beauty of a painting can be seen, and experienced, the true beauty comes from within- by asking yourself the tough questions, do the work to stretch and grow, and allowing yourself the confidence to make your dreams a reality. Today I continue to live life unfiltered with the help of brands like @loccitaneusa and their Immortelle Precious Light Cream with SPF 20, which remind me to embrace my inner beauty and know that the only filter I need is one from the sun ✨
@loccitaneusa #SPFisMyFilter #NoFilterNeeded #LoveLoccitane #LoccitanePartner

Growing up, as the oldest of four daughters there’s a common thread of constantly comparing aspects of my life to others. Of course, we all have our highs and lows — we can all relate to the roller coaster that is self-confidence, especially as women. 
But, with time comes lessons learned and wisdom that teach us you can only spend so long comparing yourself to others and wanting what you don’t have. Over the years navigating the fashion industry and experimenting with my wardrobe, beauty routines and beyond,  I’ve come into my own and learned to love even the things I used to hate. The things that really matter and separate me from the crowd, like my love and knowledge of fashion, style, and fine arts- which has always brought great joy to my life. And that’s what’s important — beauty isn’t only external, beauty exists in our passions, insecurities and our ability to overcome obstacles. That’s something @loccitaneusa understands with their new Immortelle Precious Light cream now with SPF 20, that as women we should live our lives unfiltered- glowing from the inside out. If only my younger self could see me now she’d see that I need no filter but SPF. 😉  Tagging my gorgeous sister, and favorite mama @nicolette.ivy who inspires me daily! And I want to encourage all of you to tag a woman that inspires you in the comments! 
#NoFilterNeeded #SPFIsMyFilter #LoccitanePartner #LoveLoccitane
